import React, { FC } from "react"
import { Route } from "react-router-dom"
import { Profile } from "../Profile/Profile"
import { ProfileNav } from "../ProfileNav/ProfileNav"
import { ProfileContent } from "./ProfileContent"
import { News } from "../News/News"

import { postProps } from "../../App"

type props = {
  toggle: (id: number) => void
  postNews: postProps[]
}

export const Content: FC<props> = ({ toggle, postNews }) => {
  return (
    <>
      <Profile />
      <ProfileNav />
      {/* <ProfileContent toggle={toggle} postNews={postNews} /> */}
      <Route path="/Tweets" component={() => <News postNews={postNews} toggle={toggle} />} />
      <Route path="/Profile" component={() => <News postNews={postNews} toggle={toggle} />} />
      <Route path="/" component={() => <News postNews={postNews} toggle={toggle} />} exact />
      <Route path="/Tweets and replies" component={TweetsAndRepliesTest} />
      <Route path="/Likes" component={LikesTest} />
      <Route path="/Media" component={MediaTest} />
    </>
  )
}
